{"tid":802224,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：表現繼續無改善　美國將退出世貿","createTime":"2018-09-01T10:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T11:08:56.000Z","uid":147097,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ba2f8a6c9d408ede973126169c9ff6fd3ef70e","tid":802224,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:01:25.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰如火如荼之際，美國總統特朗普周四（30日）在白宮接受彭博社訪問時指，若世界貿易組織（WTO）的表現沒有變好，美國將會退出。特朗普曾多次公開批評WTO，指該組織對待美國非常差，期望它改變處事方式。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾公開抱怨中國經濟力量強大，卻被WTO視為發展中國家，因而享有巨大的額外津貼及好處，指控WTO「不恰當及差劣地對待美國」；又要求審視其成員國地位的同時，並批評世貿無力解決紛爭。 <br />\n<br />\n世貿的爭端解決機制，負責調解各國的貿易糾紛及作出最後裁決。特朗普要求世貿改革爭端解決委員會（DSB）；美方此後多番拒絕委任DSB法官，令機構只餘3名法官，僅僅符合開庭聆訊的最低要求，貿易外交官及律師紛紛批評美國在世貿製造危機。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7569c026805604bc8efc30966be263f842df188b","tid":802224,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36810a6eee67ea4bbfb62bfd3b0d7931ad242103","tid":802224,"uid":67043,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"最終只會導致中國成為WTO唯一成員國<br />\n成為最後贏家"},{"pid":"5006a75cc4d8dd343e7273f1bd980d81c1f0c89c","tid":802224,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa74ff741033b34668b169463bf78ce90682fea3","tid":802224,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36810a6eee67ea4bbfb62bfd3b0d7931ad242103","tid":802224,"uid":67043,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"最終只會導致中國成為WTO唯一成員國<br />\n成為最後贏家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31b89122975052cd8ef2165e192cec872b324d2","tid":802224,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36810a6eee67ea4bbfb62bfd3b0d7931ad242103","tid":802224,"uid":67043,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"最終只會導致中國成為WTO唯一成員國<br />\n成為最後贏家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b678e48a25b80cce9b895d133a2b657a013615","tid":802224,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"崩盤"},{"pid":"f1e07dd4f0a8a36205a33195d5e5555e8b3217d6","tid":802224,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"敗走wto?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國：WFC wto？<br />\n真係好多人未知呢個世界邊個打骰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21708cc34c5622a5b8e47bba44fe096bf7f6ebc","tid":802224,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:08:56.000Z","msg":"美國拉隊走人<br />\n（中國）世界貿易組織"}]}